    - USD 16.4407 per right (10,837 rights on 25/06/2025)  
    - AUD 25.3011 per right (3,519 rights on 25/06/2025)

- **Post-cessation issued capital**:

**Material Impact**: Negligible dilution impact (minor lapses/cash settlements); no change to outstanding ordinary shares.  

*(Note: All figures reflect Q2 2025 activity)*
